---
title: Denver Tax Attorneys - Anderson & Jahde
desc: Helping Colorado Taxpayers and Professionals Since 1995

mast: home

pagination:
  data: collections.article
  reverse: true
  size: 3
  alias: articles
---

<section class="container mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
  <div>
    <p class="subtitle">About the Firm</p>
    <h2 class="heading my-6">Experience that only comes from doing it every day.</h2>
    <p>Individuals and businesses confronted with the IRS and state taxing authorities face potentially serious consequences. The technical world of tax disputes is not for the inexperienced — mishandling a tax controversy can be devastating.</p>
    <p>Our attorneys, including former IRS trial lawyers, have solved countless tax problems since opening our doors in Denver in 1995. Solutions as unique as each client.</p>
    <p>
      <a class="button mt-8" href="/who-we-are">Meet the Attorneys</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-8">
      {% set items = [
        ["Lawyer of the Year &mdash; Tax Law, Denver Area", "2023 Recognition", "Best Lawyers in America &bull; Steven Anderson"],
        ["James E. Bye", "Lifetime Achievement Award", "Colorado Bar Association Tax Law Section &bull; 2021"],
        ["Named Among the Best Law Firms in America", "Recognition", ""]
      ] %}
      {% for title, subtitle, text in items %}
      <li>
        <p class="subtitle">{{ subtitle }}</p>
        <h3 class="heading">{{ title | safe }}</h3>
        <p>{{ text | safe }}</p>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-ajblue text-white py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <h2 class="heading-l uppercase">What We Do</h2>
    <span class="block border-b-2 border-b-white w-1/2 mt-4 mb-12"></span>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 gap-y-16">
      {% for area in practiceAreas %}
      <div>
        <h3 class="heading uppercase">{{ area.title | safe }}</h3>
        <span class="block border-b-2 border-b-white w-1/2 my-4"></span>
        <p>{{ area.text | safe }}</p>
        <a class="button mt-4" href="{{ area.url }}">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container mx-auto text-center">
  <h3 class="subtitle">Client Reviews</h3>
  <p class="stars text-[48px] tracking-widest"><span class="text-gold">★★★★★</span></p>
  <p class="text-sm uppercase">5.0 &bull; Google reviews</p>
  <blockquote class="lg:w-2/3 xl:w-1/2 mx-auto my-8">
    <span class="heading">"Steve Anderson and Jerry Borison are exceptional professionals who know how to solve complex IRS tax issues in a timely and effective manner. Their knowledge is unmatched."</span>
  </blockquote>
  <cite>Michael R. &bull; Google Review</cite>
</section>

<section class="bg-ajblue text-white py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="heading mb-4">Ready to resolve your tax problem?</h2>
    <p>Our attorneys are available for confidential consultations. The sooner you act, the more options you have.</p>
    <a class="button mt-8 mb-4" href="/contact">Get a Free Consultation</a>
    <p class="subtitle">Or call directly: <a href="tel:{{ site.phone }}">{{ site.phone }}</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container mx-auto">
  <h2 class="heading-l text-center mb-12">Recent Articles</h2>

  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    {% for article in articles %}
    <div class="bg-ajllgrey p-6">
      <h3 class="heading-s">{{ article.data.title }}</h3>
      <time class="inline-block font-strong my-2" datetime="{{ article.date | datetime }}">{{ article.date | date }}</time>
      <p>{{ article.data.excerpt }}</p>
      <a class="button mt-4" href="{{ article.url }}">Read more</a>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
